[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Match-rate disparity threshold: 0.10.** If any cohort's auto-attach rate differs from the population mean by more than 10 percentage points, an alert fires.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Auto-attach precision disparity threshold: 0.05.** If any cohort's auto-attach precision (measured against the gold set) differs from the population mean by more than 5 percentage points, the cohort's thresholds need recalibration.
